description:
Hi everyone,

Apologies, we couldn't find a venue for November's Meetup 😥.

However, we have a venue agreed for January and 2 speakers 💃. We will publish the event soon.

In the meantime, let's go for a social! we can talk MLOps with some drinks.

[Venue Menu](http://www.lhgbrewpub.com/our-food)

Looking forward to seeing everyone!
Jose
